# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTES
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 1. Replace all placeholder values with actual secure values
# 2. Generate secure random strings for SECRET_KEY and JWT_SECRET
# 3. Use strong passwords for database and admin accounts
# 4. Configure your actual domain names
# 5. Set up proper SMTP credentials for email notifications
# 6. Configure analytics and monitoring as needed
# 7. Adjust scaling parameters based on expected load

